3\times\frac12+4\times\frac14+5\times\frac18+\cdots=\sum_{n=1}^\infty\frac n{2^n}+\sum_{n=1}^\infty\frac2{2^n}=2+2=4
1\times\frac12+2\times\frac14+2\times\frac18+3\times\frac1{16}+3\times\frac1{32}+\cdots=\sum_{n=2}^\infty\frac n{2^{2n-1}}+\sum_{n=1}^\infty\frac n{2^{2n-2}}\\=\frac34+\frac12=\frac54
\frac{4-\frac54}2=\frac{11}8
